## Key Features
- Multi-brand TV support (Roku, Samsung, LG, Sony, etc.)
- Network discovery using Bonjour/mDNS and SSDP
- Real-time remote control commands
- Connection state management
- Error handling and logging
- Modern SwiftUI/UIKit hybrid approach

